<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Locklan 'Locky' Gilbert chose Irena Srbinovska as his winning contestant during The Bachelor's emotional finale on Thursday.</p>

<p>And a day later, the 31-year-old tattooed hunk revelled in their newfound love, sharing a very sappy post to his Instagram feed.</p>

<p>Alongside several photos of the pair next to a campervan in the outdoors, Locky told his fans that he's 'so happy right now' and has 'everything he'll ever need'. </p>

<p>'So happy right now!' Locky Gilbert shared a VERY sappy Instagram post (pictured) with Bachelor winner Irena Srbinovska on Friday, as they revel in their newfound love</p>

<p>'Yep I'm set, everything I'll ever need right here. Van, bike, swag, girlfriend and the outdoors,' Locky wrote in the caption, alongside the hashtag 'so happy right now'.   </p>

<p>In the photos, the former Australian Survivor star could not wipe the smile off his face as he enjoyed quality one-on-one time with Irena, 31.</p>

<p>One particular shot saw a casually dressed Locky wrapping his arms around Irena's slender frame, as they stood beside the campervan.</p>

<p>Smitten: Alongside several photos of the pair next to a campervan in the outdoors, Locky, 31, told his fans that he's 'so happy right now' and has 'everything he'll ever need' in Irena, 31</p>

